[I] Mail delivery agent with filtering abilities

[T] Maildrop is the mail filter/mail delivery agent used by the Courier
[T] mail server, but it can be used with other mail servers, too.

[U] https://www.courier-mta.org/maildrop/

[A] Sam Varshavchik <mrsam@courier-mta.com>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/server

[F] FPIC

[L] GPL
[V] 4.0.1
[P] X -----5---9 139.900

[D] f63ddcdee40306943df08a3e5b6f5bb9b2ad903bb9ca5e1c6f90c975 maildrop-4.0.1.tar.bz2 https://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/courier/

var_append confopt ' ' --with-devel
var_append confopt ' ' --enable-syslog=1

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -lpcre

var_append INSTALL_WRAPPER_FILTER '|' \
	   "sed -e 's,.*man.*/deliverquota.8,/tmp/,' \
		-e 's,.*man.*/maildirmake.1,/tmp/,' \
		-e 's,.*bin.*/deliverquota,/tmp/,' \
		-e 's,.*bin.*/maildirmake,/tmp/,'"
